OL,3,CBritish couple latest to be named as
OL,4,Cvictims of Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FA British couple are the latest to be
OL,7,Fnamed as victims of a wildfire in
OL,8,Fsouthern Spain.
OL,10,FSeven Brits have died, as well as six
OL,11,Fothers, following a wildfire in Bedar,
OL,12,Fin the Almeria province in southern
OL,13,FSpain, Spanish police confirmed last
OL,14,Fweek.
OL,16,FChristine and Michael Chard,
OL,17,Foriginally from the UK, were named
OL,18,Flocally to have died in the fire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
