OL,3,CBritish couple latest to be named as
OL,4,Cvictims of Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FIn a Facebook post, Christine's
OL,7,Fcousin, Sarah Gilliam, said they are
OL,8,F"heartbroken" and recalled "happy
OL,9,Fmemories" of visiting the couple in
OL,10,FBedar.
OL,12,FOther Brits who have died include Ian
OL,13,FJarvis, Pete and Fran Gillam, and
OL,14,FAnnette Kilgour.
OL,16,FA 93-year-old woman, who has not yet
OL,17,Fbeen named but is believed to be
OL,18,FBritish, died in hospital following
OL,19,Finjuries she had sustained in the fire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
