CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784575122
OL,3,CBritish couple latest to be named as
OL,4,Cvictims of Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FOn social media, Elaine Gaffney, a
OL,7,Ffriend of Ian Jarvis, described him as
OL,8,F"our lovely, funny, kind friend".
OL,10,FAnnette Kilgour, and her partner,
OL,11,FMalcolm Timbrell, moved out to Bedar
OL,12,Fafter finding their dream home on the
OL,13,Freality TV show, A Place in the Sun.
OL,14,FOn July 14, it was announced by locals
OL,15,Fthat she had died in the wildfire.
OL,17,FA Place in the Sun presenter, Leah
OL,18,FCharles-King, paid tribute to Annette,
OL,19,Fsaying on X: "I had the privilege of
OL,20,Fhelping Annette & Malcolm find a dream
OL,21,Fhome on _aplaceinthesun.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
