CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784575122
OL,3,CBritish couple latest to be named as
OL,4,Cvictims of Spanish wildfire
OL,6,F"My deepest condolences go to Malcolm,
OL,7,FAnnette's family & friends & everyone
OL,8,Faffected."
OL,10,FThe blaze, which scorched around 35
OL,11,Fsquare miles of forest and farmland,
OL,12,Fhas now been brought under control.
OL,14,FLocals are attempting to rebuild their
OL,15,Flives and arrange funerals for the
OL,16,Fpeople they have lost in their
OL,17,Fcommunity.
OL,19,FSpain has suffered from multiple
OL,20,Fwildfires this past fortnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
