OL,3,CBritish couple latest to be named as
OL,4,Cvictims of Spanish wildfire
OL,6,FAlmost 350 firefighters tackled a
OL,7,Fwildfire in La Mierla, Guadalajara,
OL,8,Fwhich scorched more than 12,000
OL,9,Fhectares on Sunday, authorities
OL,10,Fconfirmed. The fire is not yet under
OL,11,Fcontrol.
OL,13,FFirefighters managed to put out a
OL,14,Fblaze which broke out in the Zaragoza
OL,15,Fprovince on Wednesday, destroying
OL,16,F15,400 hectares of land.
